title: Error on import
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Operating System

macOS 11.6

### DeepLabCut version

I can't `import deeplabcut`, so I can't get the version # from there, but:

```
pip freeze | grep "deeplabcut"
deeplabcut==2.2.0.2
```

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type


```
sysctl -n machdep.cpu.brand_string
Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-9750H CPU @ 2.60GHz
```

### Steps To Reproduce

1. Create a new environment with python 3.6
2. Install using `pip install "deeplabcut[gui]"
3. start a new notebook in Jupyter Lab, selecting the kernel from the environment we just created 
4. Try `import deeplabcut`
